name: Sideways Cross Necklace
description:
Gold plated sterling silver sideways Cross necklace is inspired by jewelry worn by celebs like Jessica Biel and Michelle Williams. - Simple gold plated silver Cross is connected at the "top" and "bottom" with gold chains, so it hangs as though a traditional Cross has been rotated 90 degrees to the right. - Cross is fixed on the gold chain, which is adjustable from 17.5-19 inches. - Available in sterling silver gold plated sterling silver or Hematite.

Please note - pendant is fixed on the chain and cannot be removed.

Can be worn alone or stacked for a more full look!
